title: Melanie C - Sporty's Forty DVD (DVD9)
description:
To celebrate her 40th birthday, Melanie C threw a very special birthday party. The night before Sporty turned forty, Melanie and her band played a live show at London's Shepherd's Bush Empire. To remember that and celebrate the 15th anniversary of her debut solo album, Northern Star, here's another party! On Saturday evening, October 18th, a special one-off video webcast of Melanie's 'Sporty's Forty' Shepherd's Bush Empire concert was broadcasted.
The program is just over two hours and includes all 23 songs Melanie performed at Shepherd's Bush Empire in January, as well as a short interview in which Melanie talks about her birthday bash. The event was streamed live through YouTube. #SportysFortyWebcast
